# 1. 人类基因组的大小以及基本组成

* 大小：3,280,481,986 Base Pairs，约3.2G
  
  > Genome assembly GRCh38.p14, Feb 3, 2022 
  > 
  > Alexander et al., Nature Reviews, 2010

* 基本组成：
  
  * 编码序列(Coding Sequences)
  
  * 非编码序列(Non-coding Sequences)
  
  * 重复序列(Repetitive Elements)
  
  * 功能性非编码区域(Functional Non-coding Regions)

# 2. 基因中的非编码RNA的最新注释

- 注释个数（不包含假基因）：
  
  - 46,695
    
    > Genome assembly GRCh38.p14(Primary Assembly), Aug 26 2024
  
  - 49,289
    
    > Genome assembly GRCh38.p14, Aug 26 2024

- ncRNA细分种类及其数目
  
  > Genome assembly GRCh38.p14(**Primary Assembly***), Aug 26 2024
  
  | 类型             | 数目     | 解释                                                                                                                                                                                     |
  |:--------------:|:------:|:--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------:|
  | miRNA          | 11,795 | Involved in RNA silencing and post-transcriptional regulation of gene expression. Reducing translation of the mRNA into proteins via shortening the poly(A) tail of target mRNA.       |
  | tRNA           | 431    | Serves as a link between mRNA and the growing chain of amino acids that make up a protein.                                                                                             |
  | lncRNA         | 30,104 | involved in various regulatory roles, including transcriptional and post-transcriptional gene expression modulation, by interacting with chromatin, proteins, and other RNA molecules. |
  | snoRNA         | 1,194  | Involved in chemical modifications of other RNAs, primarily rRNA.                                                                                                                      |
  | snRNA          | 152    | Play a key role in the splicing of pre-mRNA.                                                                                                                                           |
  | rRNA           | 37     | Core structural and functional components of ribosomes.                                                                                                                                |
  | misc_RNA       | 12,179 | A series of miscellaneous small RNA, **includes coding and non-coding RNAs**.                                                                                                          |
  | vault_RNA      | 4      |                                                                                                                                                                                        |
  | telomerase_RNA | 1      | a component of telomerase, the enzyme used to extend telomeres                                                                                                                         |
  | RNase_MRP_RNA  | 1      |                                                                                                                                                                                        |
  | RNase_P_RNA    | 1      |                                                                                                                                                                                        |
  | Y_RNA          | 1      |                                                                                                                                                                                        |
  | scRNA          | 4      | small conditional RNA                                                                                                                                                                  |
  
